<h2 id="about">About</h2>
<p>Binary Tree Partition (BTP) is a novel combinatorial formulation of the problem of constructing the subpopulations of tumor cells from the variant allele frequencies of somatic mutations.</p>

<p><a href="simple.jpg"><img src="simple.jpg" style="width: 600px" /></a></p>

<p><a name="download"></a></p>

<h2 id="downloads">Downloads</h2>
